game_description: Warning: Mild Language From Online Players. Our Moderation Team will situate that, if needed. This game is a Skiing and Snowboarding game! You can chill out and drink some hot coco in the Lounge, Ski or Snowboard alone or With Friends! You can customize your character in the shop or even buy new snow gear! If you'd like to try out Snowy Alps, Download Now! Available now for Quest, Quest 2 and Quest Pro!
